-- STEWARDSHIP (expanded)
('Moreover it is required in stewards, that a man be found faithful.', '1 Corinthians 4:2', 'stewardship_and_wisdom', 'Faithfulness is the measure of stewardship', 'Manage DeFi positions with consistent accountability', 'Smart contract governance requires faithful stewardship of protocol funds', ARRAY['stewards', 'faithful', 'required']),
('His lord said unto him, Well done, thou good and faithful servant: thou hast been faithful over a few things, I will make thee ruler over many things.', 'Matthew 25:21', 'stewardship_and_wisdom', 'Faithful small management leads to greater responsibility', 'Start with small DeFi positions and grow with proven faithfulness', 'Progressive position sizing based on demonstrated competence', ARRAY['faithful', 'servant', 'ruler', 'few things', 'many things']),
('For unto every one that hath shall be given, and he shall have abundance: but from him that hath not shall be taken away even that which he hath.', 'Matthew 25:29', 'stewardship_and_wisdom', 'Use it or lose it principle', 'Actively deploy capital rather than letting it sit idle', 'Idle capital loses value to inflation; deploy in yield-bearing positions', ARRAY['given', 'abundance', 'taken away']),
('The soul of the sluggard desireth, and hath nothing: but the soul of the diligent shall be made fat.', 'Proverbs 13:4', 'stewardship_and_wisdom', 'Diligence produces results, laziness produces nothing', 'Research and actively manage your DeFi portfolio', 'Active yield optimization outperforms passive holding', ARRAY['sluggard', 'diligent', 'nothing', 'fat']),
('Prepare thy work without, and make it fit in the field; and afterwards build thine house.', 'Proverbs 24:27', 'stewardship_and_wisdom', 'Establish income before spending', 'Build yield-generating positions before luxury spending', 'Establish stable yield streams before leveraged or speculative positions', ARRAY['prepare', 'work', 'field', 'build', 'house']),
('Which of you, intending to build a tower, sitteth not down first, and counteth the cost, whether he have sufficient to finish it?', 'Luke 14:28', 'stewardship_and_wisdom', 'Count the cost before committing', 'Calculate total costs including gas, slippage, and IL before entering positions', 'Full cost analysis for DeFi transactions including gas optimization', ARRAY['build', 'tower', 'cost', 'sufficient']),
