-- TITHING & GIVING (expanded)
('Bring ye all the tithes into the storehouse, that there may be meat in mine house, and prove me now herewith, saith the LORD of hosts, if I will not open you the windows of heaven, and pour you out a blessing.', 'Malachi 3:10', 'tithing_and_giving', 'Test God''s faithfulness through tithing', 'Tithe consistently and watch God provide abundantly', 'Automated Superfluid tithe streams with yield-boosted returns', ARRAY['tithes', 'storehouse', 'windows', 'heaven', 'blessing', 'pour']),
('Every man according as he purposeth in his heart, so let him give; not grudgingly, or of necessity: for God loveth a cheerful giver.', '2 Corinthians 9:7', 'tithing_and_giving', 'Give willingly from the heart', 'Set giving levels you can sustain joyfully', 'Customizable tithe percentages that users set voluntarily', ARRAY['purposeth', 'heart', 'give', 'grudgingly', 'cheerful', 'giver']),
('And all the tithe of the land, whether of the seed of the land, or of the fruit of the tree, is the LORD''s: it is holy unto the LORD.', 'Leviticus 27:30', 'tithing_and_giving', 'The tithe belongs to God', 'Tithe is not optional; it is returning what belongs to God', 'First 10% of all yield claims routed to tithe destinations', ARRAY['tithe', 'land', 'seed', 'fruit', 'holy', 'LORD']),
('And he looked up, and saw the rich men casting their gifts into the treasury. And he saw also a certain poor widow casting in thither two mites. And he said, Of a truth I say unto you, that this poor widow hath cast in more than they all.', 'Luke 21:1-3', 'tithing_and_giving', 'God values proportional generosity over absolute amounts', 'Give proportionally regardless of portfolio size', 'Percentage-based tithing ensures fairness across all portfolio sizes', ARRAY['rich', 'gifts', 'treasury', 'widow', 'mites', 'more']),
